Notes: This column contains free text or string identifiers for each measurement, best mapped to the 'hasFreeText' property, which expects an XML Schema string datatype.
Patient identifiers are represented via 'hasSubjectPseudoIdentifier', linking the measurement to a pseudo-identifier for the patient.
Measurement codes are captured using 'hasCode', which links to a Code entity representing the measurement's code.
Measurement values are quantitative and best represented via 'hasQuantity', which includes numerical values and units.
The unit of measurement is linked via 'hasUnit' within the 'hasQuantity' structure, representing the measurement's unit.
Measurement date is captured via 'hasMeasurementDateTime', which expects an XML Schema dateTime datatype.
